lines.text:
[spins a 14 on the Penalty Wheel and pulls the card revealing his penalty]
Oh no. Not that! Not the Gesundheit!

[spins 36 on the wheel and goes into spasms when he sees what it is]
Roll Out The Barrel. Oh No. Not that. No, not Roll Out The Barrel! Please.

[after repeatedly losing and enduring 'penalties']
Come on. Deal 'em out. Gimme the cards, deal 'em out, deal 'em out, deal 'em out...

[interrupting]
You're too unlucky cat. I'm quitting before ya kills yourself!
Don't let that stop ya, cat. I'll play ya. Step right up and cut for high card. Okay, you first.

[cuts a deuce]
Oops. No, not that. Not the Post! Oh no. Not that! Not the Post!
[cat starts swatting with a rolled up Post newspaper]
